appearance is not standardised yet. webkitAppearance works as expected. https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/-moz-appearance

resize does appear to be missing (although it is still technically working draft). If you want to add it to your own version, add this to externs/w3c_css.js:

/**
 * @type {string}
 * @see http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-ui/#resize
 */
CSSProperties.prototype.resize;

maybe somebody will add it to the main code.
